{"tid":1307084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"713 -- Christians Assemble","createTime":"2019-07-11T11:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:07:09.000Z","uid":56052,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e67b811cd73ba0aea547999da5e728e99fb7b9a","tid":1307084,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係我開po<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">大家好，我係基督徒、和理非，我都好攰&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242171\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242171</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">勇武派們，多謝您。接下來你地休息嘅時候，係和理非嘅回合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284394\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284394</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多謝大家之前嘅打氣同認同，喺呢個月，我一齊都係作為一個參加者嘅角色，去鼓勵身邊嘅同路人出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>今日，我連同一班有心力嘅基督徒，走出嚟做搞手</strong></span><br />\n我地唔希望再成為一個被動嘅角色<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地應承過呢段時間俾空間勇武嘅兄弟休息</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地會兌現呢個承諾<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由今星期六開始</span></strong>，我地發動<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">每星期六政府山敬拜活動，直至到我地每一分體力被耗盡為止</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>勇武嘅兄弟用生命為我地出嚟爭取不可多得嘅自由，唔通我地基督徒連每星期走出嚟唱詩敬拜嘅熱誠都負出唔到？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n敬拜係在乎我地嘅心思意念，唔受限於教會內。只要你有感動，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">漫山遍野</span></span></strong>都係聖殿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5aVcWbv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5aVcWbv.jpg&h=f0bc3e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今個星期六，我地會自發發起「與神同行」唱詩敬拜，希望將唔同嘅詩歌帶到「政府山」，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呼喚當權者歸回上帝</span></span>，同時藉着以詩歌，淨化大家現時心中負面情緒，尋回希望<br />\n<br />\n日期：13-07-2019<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：19：00至22：00<br />\n         （18：30集合）<br />\n路線：中途途經<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">律政中心</span></span><br />\n            及<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">禮賓府公眾活動區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>是次活動已獲發警方不反對通知書</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n活動喺夜晚進行，上山嘅路比較黑同窄，大家一路唱詩都要留意安全，保持冷靜克制，記住帶水！不反對通知書只到夜晚10:30，我地喺禮賓府東閘祈禱分享之後，會沿雪廠街斜路和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n走出來，叫萬民作祂的門徒。為着你心中嘅公義，為着5位烈士嘅意念，為着你地上嘅家，請你走出來，作活見證。"},{"pid":"2d3ca54fb9357d3b6920f8035ade9b14cae115d6","tid":1307084,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3682e545eebd7d23205670e3fee96f471f3b121b","tid":1307084,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ef04025acaedd2fa49b6e0d3a0f93ec0d359d8","tid":1307084,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />岩岩開錯台"},{"pid":"556310a42561d2f9584b74480a65d3c71d02a985","tid":1307084,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:58:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c8dc6b139fd76ebaa59a9799365bc63b2de37ae1","tid":1307084,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9d8e57ed4d351de5e022d20dfd1498187e43a3a8","tid":1307084,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"幫推!"},{"pid":"dba5e43b00c102ffe0870e769a26262d14fc63b3","tid":130708